title: Wi-Fi
description: Free Wi-Fi service is available in all public passenger areas of Terminals 2 and 4, including ticketing, baggage claim, gate areas and food concessions. Wi-Fi service is also available in the Ground Transportation Center.  Account usage is limited to 2 hours per day.

title: Rental Cars
description:
Consolidated Rental Car Facility (ConRAC)

Airport shuttles transport rental car customers between the passenger terminals and the Consolidated Rental Car Facility (ConRAC), where the on-airport rental car counters are located. Off-airport rental car companies provide transportation to customers between the ConRAC and their business location.
List of available rental car agencies

title: Accessibility
description:
Disabled parking is available in all parking lots. Terminals 2 and 4 offer accessible restrooms and elevators. Curb Cuts are provided from street to sidewalk level in front of the terminals. Wheelchairs and assistance are available through airline representatives at each airline counter.
